    Browser -- "HTTPS Requests" --> SSR
    Browser -- "REST API Calls\n(JSON)" --> APIRoutes
    SSR -- "Renders HTML" --> Browser
    VercelCloud -- "Static Files\n(CDN)" --> Browser

    APIRoutes --> DBLayer
    APIRoutes -- "HTTP POST /analyze\n(JSON Request/Response)" --> FastAPIApp
    FastAPIApp --> PriorityModel
    FastAPIApp --> AssignerModel
    FastAPIApp --> UrgencyModel
    PriorityModel -- "Loads" --> ModelArtifacts
    AssignerModel -- "Downloads on init" --> ModelArtifacts

    DBLayer -- "supabase-js SDK\n(HTTPS/REST)" --> SupabaseServices
    DBLayer --> PostgreSQL
    Auth -- "JWT Tokens" --> DBLayer
    RLS -- "Policy Enforcement" --> PostgreSQL
    Storage -- "File I/O" --> PostgreSQL

    TrainingScripts -- "Exports trained\nmodel files" --> ModelArtifacts
    TrainingScripts --> TrainingDeps
